rights lawyer in London

00:00:53.280 --> 00:00:57.390
at the European Court of
Human Rights in Strasbourg.

00:00:57.390 --> 00:01:01.410
She's published extensively on
issues of transnational child

00:01:01.410 --> 00:01:04.560
