had here the kind of solidarity

00:58:14.660 --> 00:58:16.250
that we are seeing
there, we would

00:58:16.250 --> 00:58:17.960
be in a whole other
place in terms

00:58:17.960 --> 00:58:19.685
of transnational solidarity.

