00:58:43.440 --> 00:58:45.912
out of situations of survival.

00:58:45.912 --> 00:58:47.870
And what is very interesting
is they're usually

00:58:47.870 --> 00:58:50.210
not being administered.

00:58:50.210 --> 00:58:52.280
In any resource-deprived
situation,

00:58:52.280 --> 00:58:53.605
you're going to get fighting.

00:58:53.605 --> 00:58:54.980
I mean, some people
will scrapped

00:58:54.980 --> 00:58:56.270
