on to the United Nations High

00:59:05.240 --> 00:59:07.520
Commission for Refugees and
have a certain streaming

00:59:07.520 --> 00:59:10.340
and slightly more aid--
because there was Syrian--

00:59:10.340 --> 00:59:11.990
than Palestinians.

00:59:11.990 --> 00:59:15.830
